| 7 | Previous account data after switch | `notificationPaginationProvider` with `ref.listen` inside `build()` may preserve merged state if auth change doesn't force full dispose |
| 8 | Duplicates | `attendanceWarning` has correct dedup guard. `classReminder` / `bunkPlanner` have no Firestore records at all |

