## Phase 9 ‚Äî Nightly Bunk Planner

### Current State
`scheduleSafeBunkPlanner()` schedules a device-local daily notification only. No Firestore record is written.

### Required Change
After scheduling the device notification, also write to the Firestore notification center using a deterministic daily ID:

```dart
final centerId = 'nightlyBunkPlanner_$dateKey'; // e.g. nightlyBunkPlanner_2026-06-18
final alreadyStored = await notificationRepo?.notificationExists(centerId) ?? true;
if (!alreadyStored) {
  await notificationRepo?.addNotification(AppNotificationModel(
    id: centerId,
    title: title,
    message: body,
    type: AppNotificationType.nightlyBunkPlanner,
    createdAt: DateTime.now(),
    isRead: false,
  ));
}
```

The exact message format required:
```
Tomorrow's Bunk Opportunities

You can safely skip:
‚Ä¢ DBMS
‚Ä¢ Physics Lab

Attend all other lectures.
```

Or if no bunks:
```
No safe bunks available tomorrow. Attend all scheduled lectures.
```

